OL,4,C'I can only eat once a day to make my
OL,5,Cmedication last'
OL,6,GA Kent man says he is restricting
OL,7,Ghimself to one meal a day to make his
OL,8,Gmedication last due to a shortage of
OL,9,Gthe drug.
OL,11,FPaul Elcombe, 62, from Hartley, takes
OL,12,FCreon three times a day after having
OL,13,Fpart of his pancreas removed during
OL,14,Fmajor surgery, but his supply is set
OL,15,Fto run out in 10 days.
OL,17,F"I will just fade away because you
OL,18,Fneed these tablets to digest the
OL,19,Fgoodness from the food," he said.
